@startuml
title AD-12 Submit contact form with rate limit (User vs System)
skinparam linetype ortho

|User|


start
|User|
  :Complete contact form;\nClick Send;

|System|
  :Validate fields and email format;
  if (Valid?) then (yes)
    :Check cooldown;
    if (Allowed?) then (yes)
      :POST to EmailJS;
      if (API ok?) then (yes)
        :Return success;
      else (no)
        :Return API error text;
      endif
    else (no)
      :Return remaining seconds message;
    endif
  else (no)
    :Return validation errors;
  endif

|User|
  if (Success?) then (yes)
    :See success toast;
  else (no)
    :See error or cooldown message;
  endif

stop

@enduml

